p: Anti-HIV activities of compound 150 was tested in vitro by HIV-I virus-transfected 293 T cells. At the concentration of 20 μM, 150 showed a weak inhibitory rate of 16.48 ± 6.67%. Efavirenz was used as the positive control, with an inhibitory rate of 88.54 ± 0.45% at the same concentration [ 47].
